{"tid":475640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"半山旭龢道男子兩度射擊解放軍宿舍罪成","createTime":"2017-11-21T09:55:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T16:30:51.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8ddf73dc1f820d6b82a1133d6f74673d583090ab","tid":475640,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T09:55:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171121/57486137\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171121%2F57486137&d=I3169T1L%2FPFmetaPytazgcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=631dc28c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171121%2F57486137&h=3336db3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171121/57486137</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171121/large/1511255280_3bff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171121%2Flarge%2F1511255280_3bff.jpg&h=9622e64c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n居於半山旭龢道、曾參選2011年區議會但落敗的男子方鏗強，涉嫌於2015年12月至去年1月期間，分別用丫叉把金屬彈射向解放軍宿舍，以及用氣槍把金屬彈射向解放軍高級職員官邸。方經審訊後今被裁定罪名成立，法官將案押後至下月5日判刑，期間取得被告精神科醫生報，被告須還柙小欖。被告聞言抱拳向法官連聲稱謝「好，好，多謝多謝，小欖，好！」<br />\n<br />\n方鏗強(39歲)被裁定兩項刑事毀壞及一項管有槍械彈藥罪罪成，法官裁決時引述辯方呈堂精神科醫生報告指，被告向他承認曾聽到聲音驅使他以丫叉和氣槍射擊涉案兩地點，並於事後再聽從聲音指示將氣槍丟棄，法庭認為有關說話已成證據，相信被告確有做過。<br />\n<br />\n法官亦接納醫生診斷，相信被告智力較常人低，患有自閉症及精神分裂症，但認為被告案發時聽到聲音不影響他對「對與錯」的認知，即當時被告明知錯仍行事。<br />\n<br />\n法官又指，基於在被告身上搜出的鎖匙，能開啟藏有氣槍和膠彈與金屬彈的地櫃，推論被告知悉他管有及知悉有關氣槍和彈藥已超出法例限制，故裁定被告3罪全部罪成。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情透露，被告學歷至中學，已婚並有一對子女，與家人於香港、北京和澳洲均有居所。法官表明考慮判入院令，故押後先索閱報告。"},{"pid":"15b456126c5755df11034b5fab423bf8232fccbf","tid":475640,"uid":66496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:00:20.000Z","msg":"槍王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1d092188bccaf488c392a37b96ef85175120c61","tid":475640,"uid":89955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:08:45.000Z","msg":"半山有錢低智男"},{"pid":"d2eec7087c6ea7d3fdbd4c4f81e3f4801ab5d499","tid":475640,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:11:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"877d1a860c65cba428a78e946afb63248961e661","tid":475640,"uid":20659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:13:07.000Z","msg":"勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3757a26cc2b7e828ddb9b7b1506bdddef6b10ac6","tid":475640,"uid":61300,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:19:18.000Z","msg":"弱智都有女住半山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88fcd24f88fb4b13e67f6086d6905298e7e4548e","tid":475640,"uid":59898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:22:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7699c50f203444a2a937b0599fd074bb1ef69db","tid":475640,"uid":43189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:33:38.000Z","msg":"其實扮傻都係一條好橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b9b3d8c2af5ef40961c63ce7be1fecc6f43b9d0","tid":475640,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T16:30:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實扮傻都係一條好橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前好似有人講過<br />\n扮痴線入精神病院 隨時係慘過坐監<br />\n<br />\n無精神病都比佢地醫到有精神病"}]}